<h3>Step 5: Update the Embedding Generation Script (Optional)</h3>
<p>If you want to generate embeddings for multiple sections or documents, you can modify the script to handle this. Here‚Äôs an example of how you might do this:</p>
<pre><code class="language-javascript">// ... (previous imports and setup)

